    <p class="intro-innov">  </p>
    <div class="article-content-area">
      
      <div style="padding: 20px;" class="text-center float-sm-right"><img src="/CES/media/events-experiences-images/C-Space-attendee-graphic.jpg?ext=.jpg" ></div>

<p class="intro">Advertising | Content | Entertainment | Marketing
<p>Share your content, creativity and technology with like-minded professionals in creative communications, brand marketing, advertising, digital publishing, social networking and entertainment by participating in C Space.</p>

<p>C Space is a creative, media-focused setting for networking, learning, discovery and inspiration.</p>

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -10px">Contact Us to Exhibit</h3>

<div style="text-align: center;"><iframe height="450" src="https://cea.formstack.com/forms/c_space_exhibitor_form" title="C Space Exhibitor Form" width="100%"></iframe></div>
</p>  
<div style="clear: both"></div>
<h2>Audience Insights</h2>

<p>Gain direct access to the most creative business leaders, decision makers and influencers responsible for disruptive technologies and innovation worldwide.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Participate in C Space to reach:</p>

<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
	<li>33,000+ professionals from the advertising, content, entertainment and marketing communities</li>
	<li>10,000+ senior-level executives in these targeted industries</li>
	<li>7,000+ global media attending CES</li>
</ul>

<h2><br />
Exhibiting and Sponsorship Opportunities</h2>

<p>Activate your brand through C Space with custom opportunities: meeting rooms and hospitality suites, exhibit space, VIP events and sponsored experiences, branding and promotional opportunities, and thought leadership.</p>

<p>C Space is headquartered at ARIA and features:</p>

<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
	<li>Experiential exhibits</li>
	<li>Meeting space</li>
	<li>Hospitality suites</li>
	<li>Conference sessions</li>
	<li>Lounges</li>
</ul>

<p>For additional meeting space and luxury hospitality suites, we also offer those spaces as Vdara and Park MGM, which are near the ARIA in Tech South.</p>

